  "detailed_description": "This Isn't Any Bullet Hell, It's Completely Different.<br />\r\nInspired by Beasts of Lovecraft<br />\r\n<br />\r\nShaped Beats<br />\r\nIt Is A 2D Video Game Of The Bullet Hell Genre With Pixel Art Graphics.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStory Mode (1 Player)<br />\r\nOvercome Different Challenges, Challenges increasingly difficult, and discover the secrets that exist in space<br />\r\nDefeat Different Enemies and Imposing Bosses And Discover the Truth of what happens in other worlds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVersus<br />\r\nPlay Friendly Matches With Default Settings, Or Play 1 VS 1 where you arrange how you want to play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll This And Others In Shaped Beats",
  "about_the_game": "This Isn't Any Bullet Hell, It's Completely Different.<br />\r\nInspired by Beasts of Lovecraft<br />\r\n<br />\r\nShaped Beats<br />\r\nIt Is A 2D Video Game Of The Bullet Hell Genre With Pixel Art Graphics.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStory Mode (1 Player)<br />\r\nOvercome Different Challenges, Challenges increasingly difficult, and discover the secrets that exist in space<br />\r\nDefeat Different Enemies and Imposing Bosses And Discover the Truth of what happens in other worlds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVersus<br />\r\nPlay Friendly Matches With Default Settings, Or Play 1 VS 1 where you arrange how you want to play.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll This And Others In Shaped Beats",
